{"tid":521250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(絲打入)點先叫做一個正常樣既男仔？","createTime":"2018-01-06T10:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T10:03:29.000Z","uid":84129,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2103549c8efe70f1441d465ceee2b194f32d8778","tid":521250,"uid":84129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"我係一個著衫老土，好怕醜既毒撚。我無其他人咁有自信，會覺得自己個樣真係好差。<br />\n我啲頭髮好硬，可以洗完頭，完全唔吹咁出街，比風吹都唔會郁。曾經試過all back， 但比人話太老 太成熟，好似保險佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個嘴唇好厚，略現紫色。<br />\n面形呈方形，帶圓形眼鏡。<br />\n眼睛偏細長，鼻形正常<br />\n身高168<br />\n想問一下應該點改善自己既尊容？不求變靚仔，只求變正常樣。"},{"pid":"275c9f7a7df79a6de36f9be79c56993d55f5fdc8","tid":521250,"uid":17606,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"有車 有樓 有錢"},{"pid":"2e484392666c7a39c70cb0e0e46f616c918d6bd4","tid":521250,"uid":165024,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點俾意見"},{"pid":"bfe880bbde379a2912e40939c77fdf447c06ca8a","tid":521250,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"168難搞D  同你差唔多但178"},{"pid":"b2847670d6288aaefa03530e43502d19706f54cc","tid":521250,"uid":64145,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"無身高已經無得救"},{"pid":"2ba06ce43ca9764c09777cf795b28387b3f692ef","tid":521250,"uid":84129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275c9f7a7df79a6de36f9be79c56993d55f5fdc8","tid":521250,"uid":17606,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"有車 有樓 有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"想要正常樣咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a878fdaf72f854017a7126065767a581054baacc","tid":521250,"uid":84129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe880bbde379a2912e40939c77fdf4